<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="ai.css" />
    <title>Artificial Intelligence</title>
    <style>
      .btn {
        background-color: #007bff;
        color: #ffffff;
        border: none;
        border-radius: 5px;
        padding: 10px 20px;
        font-size: 3vm;
        cursor: pointer;
        transition: background-color 0.3s;
      }

      .btn:hover {
        background-color: #0056b3;
      }

      .popup-modal {
        display: none;
        position: fixed;
        z-index: 1000;
        left: 0;
        top: 0;
        width: 100%;
        height: 100%;
        overflow: auto;
        background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7);
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        transition: opacity 0.3s, visibility 0.3s;
      }

      .popup-content {
        background-color: #ffffff;
        padding: 20px;
        border-radius: 8px;
        width: 80%;
        height: 40vw;
        max-width: 900px;
        position: relative;
        animation: fadeIn 0.3s;
      }

      @keyframes fadeIn {
        from {
          opacity: 0;
        }
        to {
          opacity: 1;
        }
      }

      .close-button {
        position: absolute;
        top: 10px;
        right: 15px;
        font-size: 2rem;
        width: 30px;
        height: 30px;
        border-radius: 50%;
        text-align: center;
        background-color: #007bff;
        color: white;
        cursor: pointer;
        line-height: 30px;
      }

      .mindmap-frame {
        width: 100%;
        height: 40vw;
      }

      .no-scroll {
        overflow: hidden;
      }

      @media (max-width: 768px) {
        .popup-content {
          width: 90vw;
          height: 60vw;
        }

        .close-button {
          font-size: 2.5vw;
          width: 4vw;
          height: 4vw;
        }
      }

      @media (max-width: 576px) {
        .popup-content {
          width: 95vw;
          height: 70vw;
        }

        .close-button {
          font-size: 3vw;
          width: 5vw;
          height: 5vw;
        }
      }

      @keyframes fadeInUp {
        from {
          opacity: 0;
          transform: translateY(2vw);
        }
        to {
          opacity: 1;
          transform: translateY(0);
        }
      }

      .ai-map {
        position: relative;
        width: 100vw;
        height: 40vh;
        opacity: 0;
        transform: translateY(2vw);
        transition: opacity 0.6s ease, transform 0.6s ease;
        background-color: #f8f9fa;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
      }

      .ai-map.visible {
        animation: fadeInUp 0.6s forwards;
        animation-delay: 0.1s;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <header>
      <div class="container">
        <div class="logo">
          <img src="https://i.postimg.cc/ryJpP5Rk/Logo-1.png" alt="Logo" />
        </div>
        <nav>
          <ul class="ul-list">
            <li><a href="/home">Home</a></li>
            <li><a href="/contact">Contact</a></li>
            <li><a href="/singn">Logout</a></li>
          </ul>
        </nav>
      </div>
    </header>

    <section class="hero">
      <div class="container">
        <h1>Artificial Intelligence</h1>
        <h2>Augmenting human capabilities to solve complex problems</h2>
        <a href="#learn-more" class="btn">Learn More</a>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="ai-intro" id="learn-more">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>What is Artificial Intelligence?</h2>
        <p>
          Artificial Intelligence (AI) is a branch of computer science that aims
          to create machines capable of performing tasks that require human
          intelligence. These tasks include learning, reasoning,
          problem-solving, perception, language understanding, and more.
        </p>
        <p>
          AI can be broadly classified into narrow AI, which is designed for
          specific tasks like facial recognition or language translation, and
          general AI, which is intended to understand and perform any
          intellectual task that a human can do.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <div class="ai-map" id="aiMap">
      <center>
        <h2>Click Below to view AI Study</h2>
        <button class="btn" onclick="showPopup()">AI MIND MAP's</button>
      </center>
    </div>

    <div id="popupModal" class="popup-modal">
      <div class="popup-content">
        <span class="close-button" onclick="hidePopup()">&times;</span>
        <iframe class="mindmap-frame" src="/mindmap"></iframe>
      </div>
    </div>

    <section class="ai-applications">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>Applications of AI</h2>
        <div class="ai-application-items">
          <div class="ai-application-item">
            <img
              src="https://www.shutterstock.com/shutterstock/photos/2284126663/display_1500/stock-photo-data-science-and-big-data-technology-scientist-computing-analysing-and-visualizing-complex-data-2284126663.jpg"
              alt="AI in Data Science"
            />
            <h3>AI in Data Science</h3>
            <p>
              AI is revolutionizing data science by enabling machines to analyze
              vast amounts of data, uncover patterns, and make data-driven
              decisions.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="ai-application-item">
            <img
              src="https://d3g5ywftkpzr0e.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/13220529/Artificial-Intelligence-in-Indonesia-The-current-state-and-its-opportunities.jpeg"
              alt="AI in Healthcare"
            />
            <h3>AI in Healthcare</h3>
            <p>
              In healthcare, AI is being used for early diagnosis, personalized
              medicine, and even robotic surgeries, improving outcomes and
              reducing costs.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="ai-application-item">
            <img
              src="https://www.mygreatlearning.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/What-is-data-science-2.jpg"
              alt="AI in Autonomous Vehicles"
            />
            <h3>AI in Vehicles</h3>
            <p>
              AI is at the core of autonomous vehicles, enabling them to
              navigate, avoid obstacles, and drive safely without human
              intervention.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="ai-future">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>The Future of AI</h2>
        <p>
          The future of AI is both exciting and challenging. As AI continues to
          evolve, it will undoubtedly transform industries, economies, and
          societies. However, it also raises important ethical questions about
          the role of machines in human lives.
        </p>
        <p>
          Ensuring that AI is developed and used responsibly will be critical as
          we move forward.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <footer>
      <div class="container">
        <p>&copy; 2024 Engineering Career Counseling. All rights reserved.</p>
      </div>
    </footer>

    <script>
      let body = document.querySelector("body");
      let popModal = document.querySelector("#popupModal");

      function showPopup() {
        popModal.style.display = "flex";
        document.body.classList.add("no-scroll");
      }

      function hidePopup() {
        document.getElementById("popupModal").style.display = "none";
        document.body.classList.remove("no-scroll");
      }

      document.addEventListener("DOMContentLoaded", function () {
        const aiMap = document.getElementById("aiMap");

        function checkVisibility() {
          const rect = aiMap.getBoundingClientRect();
          const windowHeight =
            window.innerHeight || document.documentElement.clientHeight;

          if (rect.top <= windowHeight && rect.bottom >= 0) {
            aiMap.classList.remove("visible");
            void aiMap.offsetWidth; // Force reflow to reset animation

            setTimeout(() => {
              aiMap.classList.add("visible");
            }, 0);
          }
        }

        window.addEventListener("scroll", checkVisibility);
        window.addEventListener("resize", checkVisibility);

        checkVisibility();
      });
    </script>
  </body>
</html>
